#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:1
msgid "Filling In the Tabs"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:3
msgid ""
"This page describes each tab's fields, what they map to in the generated "
"Turtle, and what validation rules apply. For the full UI field ↔ RDF "
"property mapping tables, see the [Field Mapping Reference]{1}."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:7
msgid "Service tab"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:9
msgid "The Service tab models `cpsv:PublicService`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:11
msgid ""
"**Unique identifier** (`dct:identifier`) — Mandatory. Used as the base for "
"all URIs in the file. Spaces are converted to hyphens automatically. Choose "
"a stable, human-readable value."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:13
msgid ""
"**Official name** (`dct:title`) — Mandatory. The public-facing name of the "
"service, stored with `@nl` language tag."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:15
msgid ""
"**Description** (`dct:description`) — Detailed explanation of what the "
"service does."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:17
msgid ""
"**Thematic area** (`cv:thematicArea`) — URI for thematic classification. "
"Select from the dropdown or enter a URI directly."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:19
msgid ""
"**Government level** (`cv:sector`) — Mandatory. Select from the controlled "
"vocabulary (national, provincial, municipal, etc.)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:21
msgid ""
"**Keywords** (`dcat:keyword`) — Comma-separated terms for discoverability."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:23
msgid ""
"**Language** (`dct:language`) — Outputs as a LinguisticSystem URI (e.g. "
"`https://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/NLD`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:25
msgid ""
"**Cost section** — Documents fees associated with the service as `cv:Cost`. "
"Enter amount and currency."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:27
msgid ""
"**Output section** — Documents what the citizen receives as `cv:Output`. "
"Enter a title and description."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:31
msgid "Organisation tab"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:33
msgid "The Organisation tab models `cv:PublicOrganisation`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:35
msgid ""
"**Organisation identifier** — Mandatory. Enter a short ID (e.g. `SVB`) or a "
"full URI. Short IDs are expanded to `https://regels.overheid.nl/"
"organizations/{id}`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:37
msgid "**Organisation name** (`skos:prefLabel`) — The official name."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:39
msgid ""
"**Geographic jurisdiction** (`cv:spatial`) — Mandatory. The geographic area "
"the organisation is responsible for, as a URI."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:41
msgid ""
"**Homepage** (`foaf:homepage`) — The organisation's official website URI."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:43
msgid ""
"**Logo** — Upload a JPG or PNG. The editor resizes it to 256×256px. The logo "
"URI is generated as `./assets/{OrganisationName}_logo.png` and included in "
"the Turtle as both `foaf:logo` and `schema:image`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:52
msgid "Legal tab"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:54
msgid "The Legal tab models `eli:LegalResource`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:56
msgid ""
"**BWB ID** — The Dutch legal resource identifier (e.g. `BWBR0002221`). "
"Validated against the BWB pattern. The editor constructs a "
"`wetten.overheid.nl` URI automatically."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:58
msgid ""
"**Version / consolidation date** — The specific version of the legislation "
"being referenced."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:60
msgid ""
"**Title and description** — Human-readable metadata for the legal resource."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:64
msgid "Rules tab (RPP: Rules)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:66
msgid "Each rule models `cpsv:Rule, ronl:TemporalRule`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:68
msgid ""
"**Rule identifier** (`dct:identifier`) — Mandatory. Unique identifier for "
"this rule."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:70
msgid "**Rule title** (`dct:title`) — Mandatory. Human-readable name."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:72
msgid ""
"**Rule URI** — Full URI for the rule, or leave blank to auto-generate from "
"the service identifier."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:74
msgid ""
"**Extends** (`ronl:extends`) — URI of the legal article or version this rule "
"implements."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:76
msgid ""
"**Valid from / until** (`ronl:validFrom`, `ronl:validUntil`) — Temporal "
"validity window as ISO dates."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:78
msgid ""
"**Confidence level** (`ronl:confidenceLevel`) — The certainty with which "
"this rule implements the policy."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:80
msgid ""
"Multiple rules can be added with the **Add Rule** button. Each rule appears "
"as an expandable card."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:84
msgid "Parameters tab (RPP: Parameters)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:86
msgid "Each parameter models `ronl:ParameterWaarde`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:88
msgid ""
"**Notation** (`skos:notation`) — Machine-readable identifier for the "
"parameter (e.g. `AOW_LEEFTIJD_STANDAARD`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:90
msgid "**Label** (`skos:prefLabel`) — Human-readable name."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:92
msgid "**Value** (`schema:value`) — The numeric or string value."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:94
msgid ""
"**Unit** (`schema:unitCode`) — The unit of measurement (e.g. `ANN` for "
"years, `EUR` for euros)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:96
msgid "**Valid from / until** — Temporal validity."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:100
msgid "CPRMV tab (RPP: Policy)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:102
msgid "Each entry models `cprmv:Rule`. All six fields are mandatory."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:104
msgid ""
"**Identifier** (`dct:identifier`), **Title** (`dct:title`), **Definition** "
"(`cprmv:definition`) — Standard metadata."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:106
msgid ""
"**Situation** (`cprmv:situatie`) — The contextual situation to which the "
"rule applies."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:108
msgid "**Norm** (`cprmv:norm`) — The normative value mandated by the rule."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:110
msgid ""
"**Rule ID path** (`cprmv:ruleIdPath`) — The legislative path to the source "
"article."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:112
msgid ""
"CPRMV rules can be entered individually or imported in bulk via the **Import "
"JSON** button, which accepts normenbrief-format JSON."
msgstr ""

